{
  "stem": "24462.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I wrote to the consulate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the meantime, I got some reparations from the Germans for my parents' jewelry store.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was a few thousand pounds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It wasn't a fortune.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But this, is I got.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't ask-- I asked them not to transfer the money to Israel, because it was very hard to get it out, to keep it in London, in a bank, and to transfer it as-- as soon as I say where.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the meantime, I met a couple who came from Australia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they-- I ask them, give me a name of a bank in Australia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "For example, ANZ Bank is a good one, ANZ.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Anyway, so I wrote to the consulate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I got a positive answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "A family, a healthy family with the means-- some means, and we are paying our passage, and we will be no burden to anybody.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they accepted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They wanted to see us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We came the consulate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They sent us to the doctor's.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was a procedure of three, four, five months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we got a visit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You don't know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ah, the Snowy Mountain Scheme, I understand that this was to brings water from one place to another, through the pipes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw it anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was in the making, in the structure in '63, '64, something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the border between the Victoria and New South Wales, in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --Lake Eucumbene-- [? what is it, ?] [? the ?] [? places? ?] I was there, everywhere.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mount [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kozciuszko. ?] Pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I read about this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I opened a business in Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Tell us about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
